Holiday Party PicturesForwarded by Matthew B FlemingHOUEES on PM Alexandra Saler PM To EES Distribution cc Subject Holiday Party Pictures For your convenience and enjoyment pictures from the EES Holiday Party on December are available online Please note that these pictures should be paid for personally To order photos taken at the EES Holiday Party you will need to go to wwwenronphotofetecom The home page will prompt you for a username and password but you do not need either of these On the right hand side of the home page it says search events Click on this link This will bring you to a search screen The easiest way to locate the pictures from Saturday night is to search by photographer Open the pull down list and select photofete and then click go This will bring you to a listing of events shot by the Photofete team Select one of the following options EES Holiday Balcony EES Holiday Candids EES Holiday Screen There were three photographers present and the photos taken have been posted separately to help speed up the process of finding your photo among the many taken that night Holiday Screen was set us on the first floor and the Balcony photos on the second floor over looking the party below Candids were taken throughout the entire evening ranging from making smores outside to the live performance ice sculptures Click on any of these listing and it will take you directly to the photos All pictures can be enlarged by clicking on each one and simply select size and quantity and click add to cart If there are any questions or if you experience any difficulty checking out please call the Photofete staff at Thank you and enjoy the pictures
